e` 和 `checkoutservice` 性能出现较大波动，尤其 `productcatalogservice` 的延迟显著增加。\n\n### 根因假设验证\n- **Primary Hypothesis**: 错误可能主要来源于 `productcatalogservice` 服务延迟，Pod `productcatalogservice-0` 至 `productcatalogservice-2` 均显示同步异常。\n- **次要可能性**: `checkoutservice-2` 也显示出延迟增加，应进一步关注其依赖关系和调用链。\n\n基于以上分析，我们反对初步假设的任何涉及 Node 瓶颈或 TiDB/IO 过载的问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Services `productcatalogservice` mostrou um aumento significativo no `rrt_max` e `rrt` para múltiplas instâncias, indicando problemas de latência no serviço.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"O rrt_max aumentou significativamente para `productcatalogservice-0`, `productcatalogservice-1` e `productcatalogservice-2` com proporções de mudança acima de 1.9.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod `checkoutservice-2` exibiu um aumento significativo no `rrt_max`, possivelmente afetado por dependências do serviço.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max disparou para `checkoutservice-2` com uma alteração de proporção de 1.7025.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "ProductCatalogService is the root cause due to extreme latency spikes in rrt_max during anomaly."}
